room_title: Escape room "Casino Heist" by Locked A Rochester Escape Room in Rochester (NY)
room_address: 200 Buell Rd suite A-8 Rochester, NY 14624
room_description: You have a friend on the inside who’s helping you rob the casino. Unfortunately, things didn’t go as planned and took a turn for the worst. You are surrounded by law enforcement and there is only one door you can exit through without getting caught. Can you crack the codes in 60 minutes to keep your freedom and the money? Or will you crack under pressure and walk away in handcuffs?
